column1: wake up drenched at night from sweating
wake up nightly with soaked clothes
woke in the middle of the night very hot
felt extra exhausted all the time
no longer to enjoy the occasional glass of wine or champagne b/c it makes me too drowsy
vivid dreams in the first week
symptoms like the flu, last for a couple of days
wanna go out or stay in bed
not that i'd want to be cry often; now, nothing
would doze off at work at my desk and during meetings
